headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Ulta Beauty (ULTA) After A 64% One Year Rally?
summary: If you are looking at Ulta Beauty and wondering whether the current share price still offers value, you are not alone. The stock last closed at US$661.49, with returns of 1.8% over 7 days, 10.0% over 30 days, 6.7% year to date, 63.7% over 1 year, 33.7% over 3 years and 125.6% over 5 years. Recent coverage has focused on how Ulta Beauty fits into the broader US retail sector and how investors are reassessing specialty retailers, which helps frame the current price action. This context matters...
